  <brief_title>Efficacy/Safety Study as H. Pylori Eradication of Triple Therapy for 7 Days Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>PhaseⅢ Study of A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled to Evaluate of Efficacy /Safety as H. Pylori Eradication Effect Between Ilaprazole/Pantoprazole</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Il-Yang Pharm. Co., Ltd.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Il-Yang Pharm. Co., Ltd.</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate of efficacy and safety as H.pylori eradiation effect
      between Ilaprazole and Pantoprazole triple therapy for 7 days treatment in Gastric and/or
      Duodenal ulcer patients with H.pylori positive infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate of efficacy and safety as H.pylori eradiation effect between
      Ilaprazole and Pantoprazole triple therapy for 7 days treatment in Gastric and/or Duodenal
      ulcer patients with H.pylori positive infection.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
